    <text x="400" y="145" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13">Flat rate, separate from other income</text>
    <text x="400" y="170" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13">Requires FIEA reclassification</text>
    <text x="400" y="195" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13">Losses carried forward up to 3 years</text>
    <text x="400" y="250" fill="#71717a" font-size="12">ETF listing possible (as early as 2027, per JPX)</text>
